    "title": "Principal Plant Manager at Honda Motorcycle India South Asia Partners",
    "description": "Grow your career with Honda Motorcycle India South Asia Partners! We are hiring a Plant Manager for our Ludhiana team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Honda Motorcycle India South Asia Partners:\nHonda Motorcycle India South Asia Partners is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage raw material procurement and inventory levels\n• Coordinate with design and engineering teams on product improvements\n• Ensure environmental compliance and waste management\n• Coordinate with logistics for dispatching finished goods\n• Maintain accurate production records and prepare daily reports\n• Manage supplier quality audits and vendor development\n• Ensure compliance with safety regulations and factory acts\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Any graduate with relevant experience\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Project Management\n• Proficiency in GD&T\n• Proficiency in 5S\n• Proficiency in ISO 9001\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in Quality Control\n• Proficiency in Statistical Process Control\n• Proficiency in SAP MM/PP\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Learning & development budget\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ludhiana, Punjab, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Honda Motorcycle India South Asia Partners!",
